+ ===================================================================== +
| HOL DISTRIBUTION DIRECTORY: Guide					|
+ ===================================================================== +


The latex document "guide.tex" contains a guide or style manual for
writing HOL documentation.  Authors of library documentation and
manual entries should read this carefully before writing.

People wishing to typeset the HOL manuals at their site should also
read this document.


--

2021: Note: this material is extremely old (1980s or early 90s), but
the discussion on how to write .doc files is still pertinent.
